            <description sparkle:format="plain-text"><![CDATA[Commit: d148391e0e1a57b0bb1c5d6548012e098c6f6162
Channel: beta

feat(app): Wallpaper Engine-style playlists with per-screen rotation

Add playlist data model, manager and per-screen rotator driving the
bottom-bar strip: ordered/random playback, timer/time-of-day/day-of-week/
logon timing, transition overlay, and save/open/settings sheets.

Add a video-end IPC event (VideoRenderer -> host) so timer switches can
defer until the current video finishes its loop, and track per-screen
current wallpaper in WallpaperViewModel for independent playlists.

]]></description>
